=== REQUIMENTS ===

In according to be compiled, the application needs

1) A Unix-like operating system
2) GCC compiler
3) PCAP libraries (http://www.tcpdump.org/pcap.htm)
4) NCurses (for nctcpsmash, on Debian-like distros install ncurses-devel)

=== INSTALLATION ===

From sources:

$ tar jxvf tcpsmash-VERSION.tar.bz2
$ cd tcpsmash-VERSION

Now you've got two ways to install tcpsmash:

  > 1. Using make
  
  	$ make
	# make install

  > 2. Using jam [ STRONGLY SUGGESTED -> http://www.perforce.com/jam/jam.html ]

  	$ jam
	# jam install
